file.name: nested_anyof.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: datamodel-code-generator bug example
components:
  schemas:
    Container:
      allOf:
        - type: object
          required:
            - contents
          properties:
            contents:
              type: array
              items:
                anyOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Type1'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Type2'
    Type1:
      type: object
      properties:
        prop:
          type: string
    Type2:
      type: object
      properties:
        prop:
          type: string
